Sp4vWxRShV0.title: Marshmello + Demi Lovato - OK Not To Be OK | Live from Troubadour (#SOSFEST)
Sp4vWxRShV0.description:
Marshmello + Demi Lovato perform an exclusive live set for Save Our Stages Fest from Troubadour in Los Angeles, CA. Find more #SOSFest streams at https://yt.be/music/sosfest.

Exclusive show poster from Jeffrey Everett / Rockets Are Red available here: https://bit.ly/3dHKLag
 
Save Our Stages Fest is a three-day virtual benefit festival with artists and organizations rallying to the aid of independent music venues at risk of closing their doors permanently. Featuring original performances and commentary from diverse talent across genres and shot live at iconic indie stages, #SOSFest aims to preserve our nation’s independent live music venues. The festival is raising funds for NIVA’s Emergency Relief Fund, where any member organization can apply for support - please consider helping by clicking the blue Donate button. 
 
About NIVA: Formed at the onset of the COVID-19 shutdown, National Independent Venue Association (NIVA), now represents more than 2,800 members in all 50 states and Washington, D.C. These independent venues and promoters were the first to close and will be the last to fully reopen. NIVA's mission is to preserve and nurture the ecosystem of independent live venues, promoters and festivals throughout the United States. To learn more about NIVA’s quest to gain federal funding for independent venues, visit https://www.nivassoc.org/take-action.  To learn more about the NIVA Emergency Relief Fund, visit https://www.nivassoc.org/erf.

ok5BGFOU2WY.title: Juice WRLD x Marshmello - Come and Go
ok5BGFOU2WY.description:
Juice WRLD was one of the most talented people I have ever met. We were both constantly on the same page when it came to music and the time we spent together were some of the most exciting times I’ve ever had in my entire life. Watching you take breaks to do wheelies on your dirt bike and then come back and finish a whole song in one take was normal and to be able to be on this album with you and show the world what we made together means so much to me. You were a great person and I miss you everyday man. You will live forever through your music. ❤️

Come & Go by Juice WRLD ft. Marshmello is out now: https://smarturl.it/comeandgoJW
Legends Never Die. 7/10. #LLJW🕊

localized.title: Juice WRLD x Marshmello - Come and Go
localized.description:
Juice WRLD was one of the most talented people I have ever met. We were both constantly on the same page when it came to music and the time we spent together were some of the most exciting times I’ve ever had in my entire life. Watching you take breaks to do wheelies on your dirt bike and then come back and finish a whole song in one take was normal and to be able to be on this album with you and show the world what we made together means so much to me. You were a great person and I miss you everyday man. You will live forever through your music. ❤️

Come & Go by Juice WRLD ft. Marshmello is out now: https://smarturl.it/comeandgoJW
Legends Never Die. 7/10. #LLJW🕊

Marshmello ft. Bastille - Happier (Official Music Video)
Download / Stream Happier ▶ http://marshmello.lnk.to/happier
NEW Mello™️ by Marshmello gear SHOP NOW ▶ https://www.marshmellomusic.com


When @bastilledan sent me happier for the first time I was taken back. The amount of emotion that you could feel in the lyrics was crazy. As I listened to the song more and more it reminded me of so many things I’ve been through in my life. Toxic relationships, letting go of things I didn’t want to and just situations where happiness came with a sacrifice. Recently I lost my best friend, my companion, my life long friend. I wanted this video to embrace the pain that we feel losing or sacrificing something and the cycle of life that comes with it. I hope this song and video can bring closure in any situation you may be and make us all happier 💛

PvfzqoimUpo.title: Marshmello Teaches You How To Recreate Alone & Summer
PvfzqoimUpo.description:
MARSHMELLO COURSE BUNDLE (ALONE & SUMMER) ▶ http://bit.ly/marshmellobundle
MARSHMELLO TEACHES YOU HOW TO PRODUCE ALONE ▶ http://bit.ly/marshmelloALONE
MARSHMELLO TEACHES YOU HOW TO PRODUCE SUMMER ▶ http://bit.ly/marshmelloSUMMER

In collaboration with Creator Arcade, Marshmello lays out his unique approach to dance music production and demonstrates how his tracks take shape in real time. Marshmello will teach you how to create unique sounds, experiment with synths, and turn chord structures and melodies into full arrangements. After discussing how to structure and arrange dance music tracks, Marshmello provides detailed lessons on mixing and mastering.Take a peek under the helmet as he walks you through his sessions and teaches you how he constructed his smash hits Alone and Summer step by step.

Designed for music producers of all skill levels. Includes 8+ hours of exclusive video content and access to 50+ Marshmello curated downloadable samples, 17 presets, stem and project files.


1 FOR 1
For each course sold, Creator Arcade will provide music education courses and resources to underprivileged schools and communities. 

Music is the only universal language. It's our mission to provide high-quality music production education to everyone. Music has the ability to inspire, motivate and communicate regardless of race, religion, gender or economic background. Our goal is to help everyone to pursue their passion for music.

Please nominate a school, program and/or community so we can enable the next generation of great artists.

Learn more about the 1 FOR 1 initiative here: http://www.creatorarcade.com/charity

More courses from Creator Arcade:

SLUSHII TEACHES FL STUDIO BASICS AND HOW TO PRODUCE LUV U NEED U: http://bit.ly/slushiiluvuneedu


ABOUT CREATOR ARCADE
Creator Arcade was founded on the idea that the best way to learn music is by simply making music. The premier online education platform provides fun, affordable, engaging, and inspirational online classes taught by world-renowned artists and producers, making it possible for anyone to learn from the best.

GW4Rp5zyrEk.title: BEST MARSHMELLO Moments of 2017!! Feat. Selena Gomez, Khalid, Migos +MORE
GW4Rp5zyrEk.description:
This has been an incredible year and I am grateful for each and every one of you! I got to play in so many amazing countries. From Australia, Vietnam, Indonesia, Thailand and Brazil to Mexico, China, India, Canada, United Kingdom, France, Japan and many more! I also had the privilege of being invited to play at so many amazing festivals; Coachella, Parookaville, EDC, Tomorrowland, Ultra, Bonnaroo, Gov Ball, Creamfields, Lollapalooza and the list goes on.
You showed so much love for my music videos including Summer with Lele Pons, Moving On, Find Me with Hannah Stocking and Anwar Jibawi, Blocks, and Take It Back with the Mello Fam. I also appreciate the support for my new songs, Silence with Khalid, Wolves with Selena Gomez, You & Me, Love U, and Danger with Migos! I was invited to present at the Teen Choice Awards with Bella Thorne, and to top if off I was featured in the YouTube Rewind of 2017 all because of you ❤️  So much NEW music and surprises in store for 2018. ❤️
